# set of server : 
    -> set up rest APIs
        > Posts 
            . fetch all post and by id
            . fetch posts by author id 
            . fetch post by categories
        > Login/Register api
            . login and sign up apis
            . authentication of user
            . user can subsribe as author

# FrontEnd setup
    -> login and sign up feature 
    -> page view animations using AOS library (npm i aos)
    -> routing to different pages 
    -> pages added : home , abour , contect , sign up and sign in
    -> responsive design on all pages
    -> User dashboard created 


# Redux store 
    -> PostSlice for storing all the posts fetched form the databse 
    -> authSlice for stroing the current state of user (signed in or not)
    -> userSlice for storing user information after login (username and email)
    